QuestData.Title: Squash Those Foul Odors
QuestData.Description: Grandpa always said, "A squash a week, and your tail won't reek."$b$b<Yoon subtly sniffs the air.>$b$bYup. I think it's been about a week. Could you help me plant a Jade Squash?
QuestData.LogDescription: Plant a Jade Squash in Sunsong Ranch. You can purchase seeds from Merchant Greenfield in the Halfhill Market.
